jQube Control Toolkit

The jQube Control Toolkit contains a rich set of controls that you can use to build highly responsive and interactive Ajax-enabled jQuery-based Web applications.

The jQube Control Toolkit is a project derivated from the concepts of Ajax Control Toolkit but with several improvements.

** The current project is NOT a copy and modification from Ajax Control Toolkit **
